N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 250.3 - Investigations

State Regulations

The commissioner may make, or cause to be made by a duly
authorized representative, any investigation which he or she may deem proper to
acquire necessary information from a State agency for the exercise of his
powers and duties under this Part. Notes
